Interface PhysicalObject

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    Agent, Building, Floor, Ground, Human, LandSurface, Pedestrian, Planet, Stairs, Surface, WaterSurface
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AgentImpl, BuildingImpl, FloorImpl, GroundImpl, HumanImpl, LandSurfaceImpl, PedestrianImpl, PhysicalObjectImpl, PlanetImpl, StairsImpl, SurfaceImpl, WaterSurfaceImpl

    public interface PhysicalObject
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'Physical Object'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Height
    • Mass
    • Base Class

    See Also:
    RobotMLPackage.getPhysicalObject()
